# Kraken API Credentials
# Get your keys from: https://www.kraken.com/settings/api
# 
# Instructions:
# 1. Log in to Kraken
# 2. Settings → API → Generate New Key
# 3. Permissions needed:
#    - Query Funds
#    - Query Open Orders & Trades
#    - Query Closed Orders & Trades
#    - Create & Modify Orders
#    - Cancel Orders
# 4. Copy your API Key and Secret below
# 5. Save this file as .env (no .txt, no .md)

KRAKEN_US_KEY=your_api_key_here
KRAKEN_US_SECRET=your_api_secret_here

# Dashboard Settings (optional)
DASHBOARD_PORT=3000

# ⚠️  IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# 
# - KEEP THIS FILE SECRET
# - Never share your API keys
# - Never commit .env to Git
# - Never post in Discord/forums/social media
# - Rotate keys every 30-90 days
# - Use read-only keys when possible
# - Monitor API activity in Kraken settings
#
# If you think your keys are compromised:
# 1. Delete the API key in Kraken immediately
# 2. Generate a new key
# 3. Update .env with new key
# 4. Restart the bot
